{"word":"ἀνώμοτος","slug":"ἀνώμοτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνώμοτος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὄμνυμι'><el>ὄμνυμι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>unsworn, not bound by oath</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <el>θεῶν ἀνώμοτος</el> <i>without swearing by</i> the gods, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>not sworn to</i>, <el>εἰρήνη</el> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}